{"data":[{"name":"90:1","price":"ഈ രാജ്യത്തെ (മക്കയെ)ക്കൊണ്ട് ഞാന്‍ സത്യം ചെയ്തു പറയുന്നു.","arabic":"لَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِهَٰذَا ٱلۡبَلَدِ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6024,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"lā uq'simu bihādhā al-baladi ","translations":["Nay","I swear","by this","city","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["lā","uq'simu","bihādhā","al-baladi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2640],[2,2640,3510],[3,3510,4350],[4,4350,5685]]}},{"name":"90:2","price":"നീയാകട്ടെ ഈ രാജ്യത്തെ നിവാസിയാണ് താനും.(1)","arabic":"وَأَنتَ حِلُّۢ بِهَٰذَا ٱلۡبَلَدِ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6025,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"1) 'ഹില്ല്' എന്ന പദത്തിന് നിവാസി എന്നും, അനുവാദമുള്ളവന്‍ എന്നും സ്വാതന്ത്ര്യമുള്ളവന്‍ എന്നും അര്‍ത്ഥമുണ്ട്.","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-anta ḥillun bihādhā al-baladi ","translations":["And you","(are) free (to dwell)","in this","city","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-anta","ḥillun","bihādhā","al-baladi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1740],[2,1740,3370],[3,3370,4260],[4,4260,5635]]}},{"name":"90:3","price":"ജനയിതാവിനെയും, അവന്‍ ജനിപ്പിക്കുന്നതിനെയും(3) തന്നെയാണ സത്യം.","arabic":"وَوَالِدٖ وَمَا وَلَدَ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6026,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"2) ഒരാള്‍ ജനയിതാവും മറ്റൊരാള്‍ ജാതനും ആകുന്നത് -മാതാവും പിതാവും സന്തതിയുമാകുന്നത്- പ്രജനനവുമായി ബന്ധപ്പെട്ട അല്ലാഹുവിന്റെ അതിസൂക്ഷ്മമായ വ്യവസ്ഥ പ്രകാരമത്രെ.","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"wawālidin wamā walada ","translations":["And the begetter","and what","he begot","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wawālidin","wamā","walada",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1990],[2,1990,2550],[3,2550,3725]]}},{"name":"90:4","price":"തീര്‍ച്ചയായും മനുഷ്യനെ നാം സൃഷ്ടിച്ചിട്ടുള്ളത് ക്ലേശം സഹിക്കേണ്ട നിലയിലാകുന്നു.(3)","arabic":"لَقَدۡ خَلَقۡنَا ٱلۡإِنسَٰنَ فِي كَبَدٍ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6027,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"3) ജീവിതത്തിലെ എല്ലാ നേട്ടങ്ങള്‍ക്കും നിദാനം കഠിനാധ്വാനമാണ്. ഒട്ടും അധ്വാനിക്കാനോ ക്ലേശം സഹിക്കാനോ തയ്യാറില്ലാത്തവന് ജീവിതവിജയം അസാധ്യമായിരിക്കും.","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"laqad khalaqnā al-insāna fī kabadin ","translations":["Certainly","We have created","man","(to be) in","hardship","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["laqad","khalaqnā","al-insāna","fī","kabadin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,610],[2,610,1480],[3,1480,3680],[4,3680,4130],[5,4130,5275]]}},{"name":"90:5","price":"അവനെ പിടികൂടാന്‍ ആര്‍ക്കും സാധിക്കുകയേ ഇല്ലെന്ന് അവന്‍ വിചാരിക്കുന്നുണ്ടോ?","arabic":"أَيَحۡسَبُ أَن لَّن يَقۡدِرَ عَلَيۡهِ أَحَدٞ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6028,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"ayaḥsabu an lan yaqdira ʿalayhi aḥadun ","translations":["Does he think","that","not","has power","over him","anyone","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["ayaḥsabu","an","lan","yaqdira","ʿalayhi","aḥadun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,980],[2,980,1210],[3,1210,2340],[4,2340,3480],[5,3480,4320],[6,4320,5425]]}},{"name":"90:6","price":"അവന്‍ പറയുന്നു: ഞാന്‍ മേല്‍ക്കുമേല്‍ പണം തുലച്ചിരിക്കുന്നു എന്ന്‌.(4)","arabic":"يَقُولُ أَهۡلَكۡتُ مَالٗا لُّبَدًا","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6029,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"4) റബ്ബിനെ ഭയമില്ലാത്ത ധനികരൊക്കെ അധാര്‍മികമായി ധനം ധൂര്‍ത്തടിക്കുന്നവരും അതിന്റെ പേരില്‍ പൊങ്ങച്ചം നടിക്കുന്നവരും തങ്ങളുടെ ചെയ്തികള്‍ അല്ലാഹു നിരീക്ഷിക്കുന്നുണ്ടെന്ന ബോധമില്ലാത്തവരുമാകുന്നു.","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"yaqūlu ahlaktu mālan lubadan ","translations":["He will say","I have squandered","wealth","abundant","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["yaqūlu","ahlaktu","mālan","lubadan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,880],[2,880,1940],[3,1940,2600],[4,2600,3835]]}},{"name":"90:7","price":"അവന്‍ വിചാരിക്കുന്നുണ്ടോ; അവനെ ആരും കണ്ടിട്ടില്ലെന്ന്‌?","arabic":"أَيَحۡسَبُ أَن لَّمۡ يَرَهُۥٓ أَحَدٌ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6030,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"ayaḥsabu an lam yarahu aḥadun ","translations":["Does he think","that","not","sees him","anyone","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["ayaḥsabu","an","lam","yarahu","aḥadun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1030],[2,1030,1210],[3,1210,1840],[4,1840,4140],[5,4140,5265]]}},{"name":"90:8","price":"അവന് നാം രണ്ട് കണ്ണുകള്‍ ഉണ്ടാക്കി കൊടുത്തിട്ടില്ലേ?","arabic":"أَلَمۡ نَجۡعَل لَّهُۥ عَيۡنَيۡنِ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6031,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"alam najʿal lahu ʿaynayni ","translations":["Have not","We made","for him","two eyes","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["alam","najʿal","lahu","ʿaynayni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,630],[2,630,1420],[3,1420,2020],[4,2020,5505]]}},{"name":"90:9","price":"ഒരു നാവും രണ്ടു ചുണ്ടുകളും?","arabic":"وَلِسَانٗا وَشَفَتَيۡنِ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6032,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"walisānan washafatayni ","translations":["And a tongue","and two lips","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["walisānan","washafatayni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2210],[2,2210,5825]]}},{"name":"90:10","price":"തെളിഞ്ഞു നില്‍ക്കുന്ന രണ്ടു പാതകള്‍(5) അവന്നു നാം കാട്ടിക്കൊടുക്കുകയും ചെയ്തിരിക്കുന്നു.","arabic":"وَهَدَيۡنَٰهُ ٱلنَّجۡدَيۡنِ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6033,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"5) സത്യത്തിന്റെയും അസത്യത്തിന്റെയും പാതകള്‍ തെളിഞ്ഞുകിടക്കുകയാണ്. ഒരു സംശയത്തിനും ഇടയില്ലാത്തവിധം പ്രവാചകന്മാര്‍ മുഖേന അല്ലാഹു ആ പാതകള്‍ വേര്‍തിരിച്ചു കാണിച്ചിട്ടുണ്ട്.","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"wahadaynāhu al-najdayni ","translations":["And shown him","the two ways","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["wahadaynāhu","al-najdayni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1480],[2,1480,5865]]}},{"name":"90:11","price":"എന്നിട്ട് ആ മലമ്പാതയില്‍(6) അവന്‍ തള്ളിക്കടന്നില്ല.","arabic":"فَلَا ٱقۡتَحَمَ ٱلۡعَقَبَةَ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6034,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"6) സത്യത്തിന്റെ പാത അനായാസം നടന്നുപോകാവുന്നതല്ല. അല്പം പ്രയാസപൂര്‍വം കയറിക്കടന്നുപോകേണ്ട മലമ്പാതയോടാണ് അതിന് സാമ്യം.","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"falā iq'taḥama al-ʿaqabata ","translations":["But not","he has attempted","the steep path","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["falā","iq'taḥama","al-ʿaqabata",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,360],[2,360,1210],[3,1210,2735]]}},{"name":"90:12","price":"ആ മലമ്പാത എന്താണെന്ന് നിനക്കറിയാമോ?","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلۡعَقَبَةُ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6035,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā adrāka mā al-ʿaqabatu ","translations":["And what","can make you know","what","the steep path (is)","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","adrāka","mā","al-ʿaqabatu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2150],[2,2150,3200],[3,3200,3370],[4,3370,4855]]}},{"name":"90:13","price":"ഒരു അടിമയെ മോചിപ്പിക്കുക.","arabic":"فَكُّ رَقَبَةٍ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6036,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"fakku raqabatin ","translations":["(It is) freeing","a neck","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["fakku","raqabatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,630],[2,630,1915]]}},{"name":"90:14","price":"അല്ലെങ്കില്‍ പട്ടിണിയുള്ള നാളില്‍ ഭക്ഷണം കൊടുക്കുക.","arabic":"أَوۡ إِطۡعَٰمٞ فِي يَوۡمٖ ذِي مَسۡغَبَةٖ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6037,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"aw iṭ'ʿāmun fī yawmin dhī masghabatin ","translations":["Or","feeding","in","a day","of","severe hunger","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["aw","iṭ'ʿāmun","fī","yawmin","dhī","masghabatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,420],[2,420,2280],[3,2280,2820],[4,2820,4340],[5,4340,4790],[6,4790,6195]]}},{"name":"90:15","price":"കുടുംബബന്ധമുള്ള അനാഥയ്ക്ക്‌.","arabic":"يَتِيمٗا ذَا مَقۡرَبَةٍ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6038,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"yatīman dhā maqrabatin ","translations":["An orphan","of","near relationship","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["yatīman","dhā","maqrabatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1660],[2,1660,2130],[3,2130,3595]]}},{"name":"90:16","price":"അല്ലെങ്കില്‍ കടുത്ത ദാരിദ്ര്യമുള്ള സാധുവിന്‌.","arabic":"أَوۡ مِسۡكِينٗا ذَا مَتۡرَبَةٖ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6039,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"aw mis'kīnan dhā matrabatin ","translations":["Or","a needy person","in","misery","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["aw","mis'kīnan","dhā","matrabatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,450],[2,450,2500],[3,2500,2960],[4,2960,4475]]}},{"name":"90:17","price":"പുറമെ, വിശ്വസിക്കുകയും, ക്ഷമ കൊണ്ടും കാരുണ്യം കൊണ്ടും പരസ്പരം ഉപദേശിക്കുകയും ചെയ്തവരുടെ കൂട്ടത്തില്‍ അവന്‍ ആയിത്തീരുകയും ചെയ്യുക.","arabic":"ثُمَّ كَانَ مِنَ ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُواْ وَتَوَاصَوۡاْ بِٱلصَّبۡرِ وَتَوَاصَوۡاْ بِٱلۡمَرۡحَمَةِ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6040,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma kāna mina alladhīna āmanū watawāṣaw bil-ṣabri watawāṣaw bil-marḥamati ","translations":["Then","he is","of","those who","believe","and enjoin (each other)","to patience","and enjoin (each other)","to compassion","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","kāna","mina","alladhīna","āmanū","watawāṣaw","bil-ṣabri","watawāṣaw","bil-marḥamati",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1080],[2,1080,1710],[3,1710,2140],[4,2140,3290],[5,3290,4480],[6,4480,5740],[7,5740,6790],[8,6790,8120],[9,8120,10175]]}},{"name":"90:18","price":"അങ്ങനെ ചെയ്യുന്നവരത്രെ വലതുപക്ഷക്കാര്‍.","arabic":"أُوْلَٰٓئِكَ أَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡمَيۡمَنَةِ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6041,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"ulāika aṣḥābu al-maymanati ","translations":["Those","(are the) companions","(of) the right (hand)","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["ulāika","aṣḥābu","al-maymanati",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2750],[2,2750,3770],[3,3770,5675]]}},{"name":"90:19","price":"നമ്മുടെ ദൃഷ്ടാന്തങ്ങള്‍ നിഷേധിച്ചവരാരോ അവരത്രെ ഇടതുപക്ഷത്തിന്‍റെ(7) ആള്‍ക്കാര്‍.","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُواْ بِـَٔايَٰتِنَا هُمۡ أَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡمَشۡـَٔمَةِ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6042,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"7) വലതുപക്ഷക്കാര്‍, ഇടതുപക്ഷക്കാര്‍ എന്നീ വാക്കുകളുടെ വിവക്ഷയെപ്പറ്റി മനസ്സിലാക്കാന്‍ സൂറത്തുല്‍ വാഖിഅഃയുടെ പരിഭാഷയും വ്യാഖ്യാനവും നോക്കുക.","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-alladhīna kafarū biāyātinā hum aṣḥābu al-mashamati ","translations":["But those who","disbelieve","in Our Verses","they","(are the) companions","(of) the left (hand)","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-alladhīna","kafarū","biāyātinā","hum","aṣḥābu","al-mashamati",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1220],[2,1220,2120],[3,2120,3890],[4,3890,4330],[5,4330,5330],[6,5330,7175]]}},{"name":"90:20","price":"അവരുടെ മേല്‍ അടച്ചുമൂടിയ നരകാഗ്നിയുണ്ട്‌.","arabic":"عَلَيۡهِمۡ نَارٞ مُّؤۡصَدَةُۢ","category":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad"],"ayahNumber":6043,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿalayhim nārun mu'ṣadatun ","translations":["Over them","(will be the) Fire","closed in","(20)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿalayhim","nārun","mu'ṣadatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1130],[2,1130,1910],[3,1910,5505]]}}],"chapter":["90 (Al-Balad)","Al-Balad","Surah Al-Balad","Chapter Al-Balad","Balad","Surah Balad","Chapter Balad","Al Balad","Surah Al Balad","Chapter Al Balad","Surah 90","Chapter 90","The City","البلد"],"version":{"key":"malayalam_kunhi","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"ml","version":"1.0.3","last_update":1622322000,"title":"Malayalam translation - Abdul-Hamid Haidar Al-Madany and Kanhi Muhammad","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Malayalam by Abdul-Hamid Haidar Al-Madany and K